"content": "<h2>The work of goldsmiths</h2>\n<h3>Making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19\">ISA 40:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:6-Isa41:7\">ISA 41:6–41:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:8-Jer10:10\">JER 10:8–10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14-Jer10:15\">JER 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17-Jer51:18\">JER 51:17–51:18</a></p>\n<h3>Rebuilding the wall of Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31-Neh3:32\">NEH 3:31–3:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:8\">NEH 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>The work of silversmiths</h2>\n<h3>Making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:4\">JDG 17:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23-Acts19:41\">ACT 19:23–19:41</a></p>\n<h3>Working with refined silver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:4\">PRO 25:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The work of blacksmiths</h2>\n<h3>Making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:12\">ISA 44:9–44:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Manufacturing weapons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:16-Isa54:17\">ISA 54:16–54:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:19\">1SA 13:19</a></p>\n<h2>The work of other metalworkers and craftsmen</h2>\n<h3>Making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:15\">DEU 27:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:4-Hos8:6\">HOS 8:4–8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:14-2Tim4:15\">2TI 4:14–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>The construction of the tabernacle</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:1–31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod36:2\">EXO 35:30–36:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:2-Exod39:3\">EXO 39:2–39:3</a></p>\n<h3>The construction of the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:14–22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:1–29:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></p>",
